author: Russell Brand
description:
Tucker Carlson has turned on Trump—and the reason is war. In this Streamed episode, I dive into the growing split inside MAGA as Trump signals U.S. involvement in a war with Iran. This isn’t what “America First” was supposed to mean. Tucker calls it out, Bannon tries to spin it, and Trump fires back. With Candace Owens, MTG, and even Alex Jones piling in, I ask: is this a betrayal of the anti-war promise—or just the mask slipping?
